[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He <qex>eked</qex> out by his wits an income of barely fifty
pounds.</q> <rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

